article.headline: Lipscomb 86, Fisk 62
article.story: NASHVILLE, Tenn. (AP) -- Cameron Robinson scored 16 points and grabbed 14 rebounds to lead Lipscomb over Fisk 86-62 Saturday night. Lipscomb (2-1) was also led by 19 point from James Poindexter and 13 points from Shaun Durant. Lipscomb hit 21 of 30 free throws, compared to just 8-22 from the charity stripe for Fisk. Lipscomb dominated the boards, grabbing 53 rebounds to Fisk's 22 and was also better from long range, hitting 9-23 3-pointers compared to 4-17 for Fisk. Chris Adams had 16 points on 6-14 shooting for Fisk, followed by 11 points from Marquis Patton and 10 points from Cedric Thomas.
